divs: Sighting DetailsI was in san francisco on 8-14-07 at CAMINO DEL MAR taking pictures of the ocean facing north west. So i'm sending you this photo maybe you can tell me what it is. i didnt see anything in the sky before i snapped the picture. THANK YOU roy
